review_blob: The spices of this beer are very enjoyable in the summer.  Very light on the palate. Great when paired with grilled fish!

This goes on the top of my list in regards to one of the best Belgian Strong Ales.  Very aromatic and rich flavored. I can especially taste the malt coffee and bread taste, and the herbs from the hops. Does not leave an after taste, and leaves your palate clean and refreshed.
